    { The status nibble has one of the values 0 for development, 1 to e for   }
    { betas 1 to 14, and f for release.                                       }

    { for example                                                             }
    { 0x000906000 == 0.9.6 dev                                                }
    { 0x000906023 == 0.9.6b beta 3                                            }
    { 0x00090605f == 0.9.6e release                                           }

